title: 06/11/21 DPS Hour 2 Rick Neuheisel and Mike Florio
itunes:title: 06/11/21 DPS Hour 2 Rick Neuheisel and Mike Florio
description:
Rick Neuheisel react to the new format for the College Football Playoff and says, "Hallelujah!". Rick tells Dan how much he thinks we needed this.

Mike Florio tells Dan that Aaron Rodgers is sending messages to the Packer's fans. Mike says both sides are playing the blame game.
